html(ng-app='landingpage')
  head
    title Welcome to bitbetwin.co
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(href='/components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='/components/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='/landingpage/css/style.css', rel='stylesheet')
    script(src='/components/jquery/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='/components/angular/angular.min.js')
    script(src='/components/angular-route/angular-route.min.js')
    script(src='/components/retina.js/src/retina.js')
    script(src='/js/app.js')
    script(src='/js/controllers.js')
    
  body(ng-controller='LandingpageCtrl')
    section.header.jumbotron
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12
            p.text-center.logo
              img(src='/landingpage/img/bitbetwin_logo_white.png', alt='Bitbetwin.co logo')
        .row(ng-show='response.msg')
          .col-md-12
            .alert.text-center.alert-success(ng-if='!response.err') {{ response.msg }}
            .alert.text-center.alert-danger(ng-if='response.err') {{ response.msg }}
        .row
          .col-md-7.teaser
            h1 Real-time Bitcoin Games 
            p Bitbetwin is a platform allowing you to play <strong>real-time games</strong> against other players and <strong>win Bitcoins</strong> in each round!
            p
              small
                |At the moment we are developing our first game and want to invite you to our beta program, to get early feedback from our future participants.
                |<strong>Take the chance and shape the first game with us!</strong>
          .col-md-5
            form.form-subscribe.well(role='form', ng-submit='subscribe()', name='subscribe_form', novalidate)
              h2 Apply for the beta program!
              .form-group(ng-class='{\'has-error\': subscribe_form.name.$dirty && subscribe_form.name.$invalid}')
                input.form-control.input-lg(ng-model='name', type='text', name='name', placeholder='Name', required, bs-tooltip='tooltip', data-placement='right', data-type='right', data-trigger='manual')
                span.help-block.has-error(ng-show='subscribe_form.name.$dirty && subscribe_form.name.$error.required') Please enter your name
              .form-group(ng-class='{\'has-error\': subscribe_form.email.$dirty && subscribe_form.email.$invalid}')
                input.form-control.input-lg(ng-model='email', type='email', name='email', placeholder='Email', required)
                span.help-block.has-error(ng-show='subscribe_form.email.$dirty && subscribe_form.email.$error.required') Please enter your email
                span.help-block.has-error(ng-show='subscribe_form.email.$dirty && subscribe_form.email.$error.email') Please enter a valid email
              .checkbox.input-lg
                label
                  input(ng-model='newsletter', type='checkbox', name='newsletter')
                  |Keep me up to date
              button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(type='submit', ng-disabled="subscribe_form.$invalid") Sign Up!
        .row
          .col-md-4
          .col-md-4
            a.btn.btn-outline-inverse.btn-lg.center-block.more(href='#more') More Information?
          .col-md-4
    section.container.info#more
      .row
        .col-md-4
          p.text-center
            span.fa-stack.fa-5x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fa.fa-btc.fa-inverse.fa-stack-1x
          h2.text-center Bitcoins
          p.text-center.lead
            |Play against the community and bet with Bitcoins.
            |The pot will be payed among all winners!

        .col-md-4
          p.text-center
            span.fa-stack.fa-5x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fa.fa-clock-o.fa-inverse.fa-stack-1x
          h2.text-center Time
          p.text-center.lead
            |The games a round based and have a limited time span.
            |Be prepared to bet on time!
        .col-md-4
          p.text-center
            span.fa-stack.fa-5x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
              i.fa.fa-check.fa-inverse.fa-stack-1x
          h2.text-center Fair
          p.text-center.lead
            |We'll provide statistical data about the game.
            |You'll always aware what's going on!
    section.callout.jumbotron
      .vert-text
        h1 Our Vision
    section.container.description
      .row
        .col-md-7
          h2 Hangman
          p.lead
            |Our first game is an adaption of the game <em>hangman</em>.
            |You'll need to guess the right word within the time limit to win.
            |You can buy a letter with Bitcoins and this money will go into the pot.
            |After the round, the pot will be shared among the winners and you'll directly receive your share! 
        .col-md-5
          img.img-rounded(src='/landingpage/img/teaser_hangman.png', alt='Teaser hangman', style='width: 100%')
      .row
        .col-md-5
          img.img-rounded(src='/landingpage/img/teaser_feedback.png', alt='Teaser feedback', style='width: 100%')
        .col-md-7
          h2 Feedback
          p.lead
            |We are highly encouraged to provide you with meaningful real time feedback on the game allowing you to develop stragies.
            |You'll always be aware how much money is in the pot, how many players are participating etc., and we are still figuring out how to optimize the game play.
      .row
        .col-md-12
